---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { IMAGES, SHOW_IMAGE_LABELS } from '../data/images';
---

<BaseLayout theme="keyes" title="The Keyes Company | A Century of Florida Real Estate" description="The story of The Keyes Company — Florida's largest independent brokerage since 1926, and the foundation behind Blackburn Realty Group.">

<div class="breadcrumb">
  <div class="breadcrumb-inner">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
    <a href="/about/">About</a>
    <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
    <span>The Keyes Company</span>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="keyes-hero reveal" style={`--keyes-hero-img: url('${IMAGES.keyesHero.src}')`}>
  <div class="keyes-hero-veil"></div>
  <div class="keyes-hero-inner">
    <p class="page-eyebrow">The Foundation</p>
    <h1 class="keyes-hero-title">The Keyes Company.<br/><em>Since 1926.</em></h1>
    <p class="keyes-hero-sub">Blackburn Realty Group is a division of The Keyes Company &mdash; Florida's #1 independent brokerage, family-owned for nearly a century, with a statewide footprint no boutique can match.</p>
  </div>
  {SHOW_IMAGE_LABELS && !IMAGES.keyesHero.team && (
    <div class="keyes-hero-imglabel">Image · {IMAGES.keyesHero.intent}</div>
  )}
</section>

<div class="keyes-stats reveal">
  <div class="keyes-stat">
    <div class="keyes-stat-number">100</div>
    <div class="keyes-stat-label">Years of Service<br/>Since 1926</div>
  </div>
  <div class="keyes-stat">
    <div class="keyes-stat-number">#1</div>
    <div class="keyes-stat-label">Independent Brokerage<br/>in Florida</div>
  </div>
  <div class="keyes-stat">
    <div class="keyes-stat-number">60+</div>
    <div class="keyes-stat-label">Offices<br/>Statewide</div>
  </div>
  <div class="keyes-stat">
    <div class="keyes-stat-number">4,000+</div>
    <div class="keyes-stat-label">Licensed Agents<br/>Across Florida</div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="keyes-section reveal">
  <p class="lead">When you work with Blackburn Realty Group, you are not working with a small boutique that hopes to find you a property. You are working with the infrastructure of the largest independent brokerage in the state.</p>

  <p>The Keyes Company was founded in 1926 by Kenneth Keyes Sr., a young Miami real estate broker who believed that local knowledge, family stewardship, and unwavering service would build something that outlasted him. Nearly a century later, the Keyes family still owns and operates the company &mdash; one of the only independent brokerages in America to have remained in family hands across four generations.</p>

  <p>That continuity matters. While national chains acquire, rebrand, and downsize, Keyes has built and reinvested in Florida year after year. Sixty-plus offices stretch from Key West to Jacksonville. Four thousand licensed agents serve every county. And the back-office infrastructure &mdash; legal, marketing, technology, training, compliance, and transaction management &mdash; supports every single closing as if it were the most important one.</p>
</section>

<div class="section-rule"></div>

<section class="timeline-section">
  <div class="timeline-item reveal">
    <div class="timeline-year">1926</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h3>Founded in Miami</h3>
      <p>Kenneth Keyes Sr. opens the doors of The Keyes Company in downtown Miami, focused on serving the rapid growth of South Florida during the original Florida land boom.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline-item reveal">
    <div class="timeline-year">1950s</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h3>Statewide Expansion</h3>
      <p>The company expands beyond Miami-Dade into Broward and Palm Beach, establishing the regional presence that defines the modern Tri-County market.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline-item reveal">
    <div class="timeline-year">1980s</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h3>Recognition as Florida Leader</h3>
      <p>Keyes becomes one of the largest privately-held real estate firms in Florida, earning consistent recognition as a top brokerage and trusted advisor to international buyers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline-item reveal">
    <div class="timeline-year">2000s</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h3>Multi-Generational Stewardship</h3>
      <p>The Keyes family transitions ownership across generations, maintaining the firm's independence while expanding to 60+ offices and a 4,000+ agent network across the state.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="timeline-item reveal">
    <div class="timeline-year">2026</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h3>Blackburn Realty Group Launches</h3>
      <p>Olga Blackburn establishes Blackburn Realty Group as a division of The Keyes Company &mdash; the first international team within Keyes specifically built around 50 languages, 50 cultures, and 100 vetted bilingual agents serving global buyers entering Florida.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-rule"></div>

<!-- ── KEYES LINEAGE / FOUNDERS ── -->
<section class="lineage-section reveal">
  <div class="lineage-photo">
    <img src="/images/team/keyes-founders-lineage.jpg" alt="Keyes Company leadership holding portraits of founder Kenneth S. Keyes and chairman Theodore J. Pappas" loading="lazy" />
  </div>
  <div class="lineage-text">
    <p class="section-label">Four Generations of Leadership</p>
    <h2>A century <em>in the family.</em></h2>
    <p>The Keyes Company has been led by the same family lineage for nearly a hundred years — passed down, generation to generation, without ever leaving family hands.</p>
    <p>It began with <strong>Kenneth&nbsp;S.&nbsp;Keyes</strong>, who founded the company in 1926. Leadership then passed to <strong>Theodore&nbsp;J.&nbsp;Pappas</strong>, who served as Chairman. From him it continued to his son, <strong>Mike&nbsp;Pappas</strong>, and today carries forward through his daughter, <strong>Christina&nbsp;Pappas</strong> — four generations of stewardship of Florida's largest independent brokerage.</p>
    <p class="lineage-caption">Pictured: Keyes leadership holding the framed portraits of founder Kenneth&nbsp;S.&nbsp;Keyes and Chairman Theodore&nbsp;J.&nbsp;Pappas.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-rule"></div>

<section class="partnership-section reveal">
  <h2>Why a <em>division</em>, not a startup.</h2>

  <p>Blackburn Realty Group could have launched as a standalone brokerage. We chose not to. Here is why.</p>

  <p>International buyers entering the Florida market are not looking for a brand new boutique with promising marketing. They are looking for institutional credibility, legal protection, marketing reach, MLS access, transaction infrastructure, and the assurance that the firm they trust today will still exist when they sell in fifteen years.</p>

  <p>By operating as a division of The Keyes Company, Blackburn Realty Group inherits a century of institutional weight &mdash; the legal department, the compliance team, the marketing engine, the statewide office network, and the operational discipline of one of the most respected independent brokerages in the United States.</p>

  <p>Olga Blackburn brings the international vision, the language infrastructure, and the agent-recruitment standard. The Keyes Company brings the foundation that has been quietly serving Floridians since the year Henry Ford's Model T was still rolling off the line.</p>

  <p>Together, this is what Florida real estate should look like for the global buyer.</p>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="cta-strip-inner">
    <p class="cta-strip-eyebrow">Welcome Home</p>
    <h2 class="cta-strip-headline">A century of trust. <em>50 languages of welcome.</em></h2>
    <p class="cta-strip-body">Whether you are buying your first Florida property or your fifteenth, you are backed by the infrastructure of Florida's #1 independent brokerage.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/ladies/" class="btn-primary">Find Your Agent</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn-secondary">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="mobile-sticky">
  <a href="/ladies/" class="mobile-sticky-btn">Find My Agent</a>
  <a href="/tools/preapproval/" class="mobile-sticky-btn">Get Pre-Approved</a>
  <a href="/tools/homevalue/" class="mobile-sticky-btn">Home Value</a>
</div>


<script is:inline>
  (function () {
    var els = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
    if (!('IntersectionObserver' in window)) { els.forEach(function (e) { e.classList.add('is-in'); }); return; }
    var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
      entries.forEach(function (entry) {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) { entry.target.classList.add('is-in'); io.unobserve(entry.target); }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1, rootMargin: '0px 0px -6% 0px' });
    els.forEach(function (e) { io.observe(e); });
  })();
</script>

</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
    .nav-item > a:hover { color: var(--white); }
    
    .nav-dropdown a:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .nav-dropdown a:hover { color: var(--white); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); padding-left: 30px; }
    .nav-dropdown a.ladies { border-left: 2px solid var(--pink); }
    .nav-dropdown a.guys { border-left: 2px solid var(--turquoise); }
    .nav-dropdown a.ladies:hover { color: var(--pink); }
    .nav-dropdown a.guys:hover { color: var(--turquoise); }

    /* breadcrumb */

    .breadcrumb-inner a:hover { color: var(--theme); }

    /* page hero shared */
    .page-hero {
      padding: 60px 52px 80px;
      max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .page-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.4em; color: var(--theme);
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .page-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em; color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .page-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
    .page-sub {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2.2vw, 1.5rem);
      color: var(--silver); max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* sections */
    .section {
      padding: 80px 52px;
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .section-wide { max-width: 1400px; }
    .section h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.2vw, 3.2rem);
      color: var(--white); line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .section h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
    .section h3 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.38em; color: var(--theme);
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .section p {
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.95; color: var(--silver-mid);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .section p.lead {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--silver-light);
      line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .section-rule {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent);
      max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* buttons */

    /* final cta strip */

    .cta-strip-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }

    /* footer */

    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--silver-light); }

    /* mobile sticky */
    .mobile-sticky {
      display: none;
      position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 90;
      background: rgba(6,6,6,0.97);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding: 12px 16px; gap: 8px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    .mobile-sticky-btn {
      flex: 1;
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
      text-align: center; text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 8px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      color: var(--silver-light);
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .mobile-sticky-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }

    /* mobile */
    @media (max-width: 860px) {

      .mobile-sticky { display: flex; }
      
      .page-hero { padding: 40px 22px 50px; }
      .section { padding: 60px 22px; }

    }

    .keyes-section {
      padding: 80px 52px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .keyes-section p {
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 2;
      color: var(--silver-mid);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .keyes-section p.lead {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--silver-light);
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin-bottom: 44px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .keyes-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
      background: var(--near-black);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      padding: 64px 52px;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 40px auto;
    }
    .keyes-stat {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 24px;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .keyes-stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .keyes-stat-number {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
      color: var(--theme);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(232,232,232,0.25);
    }
    .keyes-stat-label {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      color: var(--silver-dark);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .timeline-section {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 52px;
    }
    .timeline-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      padding: 36px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .timeline-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .timeline-year {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      color: var(--theme);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .timeline-content h3 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .timeline-content p {
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: var(--silver-dark);
    }

    .partnership-section {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 52px;
    }
    .partnership-section p {
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 2;
      color: var(--silver-mid);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .partnership-section h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.2vw, 2.8rem);
      color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .partnership-section h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .keyes-section { padding: 60px 22px; }
      .keyes-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); padding: 40px 22px; gap: 32px 0; }
      .keyes-stat { border-right: none; padding: 16px; }
      .keyes-stat:nth-child(odd) { border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
      .keyes-stat:nth-child(3), .keyes-stat:nth-child(4) { border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding-top: 32px; }
      .timeline-section { padding: 60px 22px; }
      .timeline-item { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 8px; padding: 28px 0; }
      .timeline-year { font-size: 1.8rem; }
      .partnership-section { padding: 60px 22px; }
    }

    /* ── KEYES ROOM: heritage library (bronze) ── */
    .keyes-hero {
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 74vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      text-align: center; padding: 140px 32px 90px;
      background: var(--keyes-hero-img) center 50% / cover no-repeat;
    }
    .keyes-hero-veil {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(6,6,6,0.70) 0%, rgba(6,6,6,0.85) 58%, var(--black) 100%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 52%, rgba(6,6,6,0.55), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 8%, rgba(var(--theme-rgb),0.18), transparent 55%);
    }
    .keyes-hero-inner { position: relative; max-width: 820px; }
    .keyes-hero-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.4rem); line-height: 1;
      color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 26px; letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .keyes-hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
    .keyes-hero-sub {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.2vw, 1.5rem); color: var(--silver);
      line-height: 1.55; max-width: 660px; margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .keyes-hero-imglabel {
      position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; z-index: 2;
      padding: 8px 14px; text-align: left;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.9), transparent);
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif; font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
    }
    /* timeline gets a bronze spine on hover */
    .timeline-item { transition: transform 0.4s; }
    .timeline-item:hover { transform: translateX(6px); }
    .timeline-year { transition: color 0.4s; }
    .timeline-item:hover .timeline-year { color: var(--theme); }
    /* stat numbers glow faintly in bronze */
    .keyes-stat-number { text-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(var(--theme-rgb), 0.25); }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(26px);
      transition: opacity 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.2,0.7,0.2,1), transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.2,0.7,0.2,1);
    }
    .reveal.is-in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .reveal { opacity: 1; transform: none; transition: none; } }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .keyes-hero { min-height: 60vh; padding: 100px 22px 60px; background-attachment: scroll; }
    }

    /* ── LINEAGE / FOUNDERS ── */
    .lineage-section {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1fr;
      gap: 56px;
      align-items: center;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 90px 52px;
    }
    .lineage-photo {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(var(--theme-rgb), 0.2);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    }
    .lineage-photo img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
    .lineage-text h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      color: var(--white); line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .lineage-text h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--theme); }
    .lineage-text .section-label {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.38em;
      color: var(--theme); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .lineage-text p {
      font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.9;
      color: var(--silver-mid); margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .lineage-text strong { color: var(--white); font-weight: 500; }
    .lineage-caption {
      font-size: 0.82rem !important;
      color: var(--silver-dark) !important;
      font-style: italic;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding-top: 18px; margin-top: 8px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .lineage-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; padding: 60px 22px; }
    }
</style>
